description:
The last time I worked with Diego he told me about his hot cousin, Antonio. He's trying to move out of his parent's house and was excited about the opportunity to make some money doing what he does best.
After a few conversations, I had Antonio rubbing one off just like his cousin.
Since it was his first time in front of the camera, he was really nervous. Antonio is a very shy person with an awesome body and a cute smile. In this case, actions speak louder than words. I really like how he knows how to work his unit.
There is definitely something to say about Argentinean uncut cocks.
title: Antonio
